node.text:
I’m happy to show you this page I made for a storybook series called Ophelia. Artists from all over the world are contributing to these adventures of this 12-year-old demigod girl with a magic paintbrush. We are aiming to get our first book out on Indiegogo this year! Website: https://www.weloveophelia.online
IG page: @team_ophelia_storybook
.
.
#watercolor #illustration #illustratorsoninstagram #detailedart #bookillustration #watercolorillustration #illustrationoftheday #illustrators
